<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'About Ultra Skool', description: 'Learn the mission, framing, and research direction behind Ultra Skool.' }) %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="main-page">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <section class="hero-shell">
                <div class="page-orb left-[-4rem] top-12 h-40 w-40 bg-purple-500/16"></div>
                <div class="page-orb bottom-[-5rem] right-[-2rem] h-56 w-56 bg-violet-500/14"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr]">
                    <div>
                        <span class="style-kicker mb-6">About Ultra Skool</span>
                        <h1 class="title mb-5">Pioneering Consciousness Engineering</h1>
                        <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-[#e0e0ff]/84 md:text-xl">
                            Ultra Skool represents the convergence of cutting-edge neuroscience and quantum consciousness exploration. We stand at the frontier of human potential, where advanced ultrasound technology meets the quantum realm of consciousness.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid gap-4">
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="section-label">Approach</p>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-white">A structured blend of theory, experimentation, and community-led investigation.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <p class="section-label">Direction</p>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-white">Research-informed exploration focused on human potential, perception, and deeper awareness.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
                <article class="section-shell">
                    <p class="section-label">Mission</p>
                    <div class="mt-5 space-y-6 text-lg text-[#e0e0ff]/84">
                        <p>Drawing from the groundbreaking research of Dr. Stuart Hameroff and other pioneers in quantum biology, we've developed unprecedented protocols for consciousness expansion. Our focus extends beyond traditional neuroscience, delving into the quantum processes within neural microtubules - the very fabric of consciousness itself.</p>
                        <p>Through our advanced ultrasound stimulation techniques and xenon-enhanced protocols, we're opening new pathways to deeper states of awareness. This isn't just about personal transformation - it's about pushing the boundaries of human consciousness and understanding.</p>
                        <p>
                            Join us at
                            <a href="https://skool.com/ultra" class="text-purple-300 underline decoration-purple-400/35 underline-offset-4 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white">Skool.com/ultra</a>,
                            where a community of consciousness pioneers awaits. Together, we're exploring the quantum frontiers of human potential.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <aside class="grid gap-6">
                    <div class="section-shell">
                        <p class="section-label">Core themes</p>
                        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                            <span class="style-chip">Quantum biology</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Ultrasound stimulation</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Microtubule research</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Consciousness protocols</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="section-shell text-center">
                        <p class="section-label">Join the field</p>
                        <p class="mt-4 font-cormorant text-3xl text-white">Step into the collective.</p>
                        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
                            <button id="cta-button" class="quantum-button w-full">Enter the Quantum Realm</button>
                            <p class="text-sm italic text-purple-300/80">Access advanced consciousness engineering protocols.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 